extension.name: t_letter
ess_marks:
misc_predict_4

Template
dir = misc
min_body_atoms = 2
max_body_atoms = 2
num_arrow_rules = 0
num_causes_rules = 1
num_visual_predicates = Nothing
use_noise = False

Frame
types = [t_sensor,t_grid,t_letter,t_object]
type_hierarchy = []
objects = [(obj_sensor,t_sensor),(obj_grid,t_grid),(obj_letter_a,t_letter),(obj_letter_b,t_letter),(obj_letter_c,t_letter),(obj_letter_d,t_letter),(obj_letter_e,t_letter),(obj_letter_d,t_letter),(obj_letter_f,t_letter)]
exogeneous_objects = []
permanent_concepts = [(p_succ,Constructed,[t_letter,t_letter]),(p_part,Constructed,[t_sensor,t_grid])]
fluid_concepts = [(c_letter,[t_sensor,t_letter])]
input_concepts = [c_letter]
static_concepts = []
vars = [(var_l,t_letter),(var_l2,t_letter),(var_s,t_sensor)]
var_groups = [[var_l,var_l2,var_s]]
aux_files = ["misc_predict_4_interpret_mem.lp"]
% misc_predict_4
% Optimization:4

% Typing
is_type(t_grid).
is_type(t_letter).
is_type(t_object).
is_type(t_sensor).
permanent(isa(t_grid,obj_grid)).
permanent(isa(t_letter,obj_letter_a)).
permanent(isa(t_letter,obj_letter_b)).
permanent(isa(t_letter,obj_letter_c)).
permanent(isa(t_letter,obj_letter_d)).
permanent(isa(t_letter,obj_letter_e)).
permanent(isa(t_letter,obj_letter_f)).
permanent(isa(t_object,obj_sensor)).
permanent(isa(t_sensor,obj_sensor)).

% Concepts
is_concept(c_letter).
is_concept(p_part).
is_concept(p_succ).
is_concept(t_grid).
is_concept(t_letter).
is_concept(t_object).
is_concept(t_sensor).

% New permanents

% Given permanents
permanent(isa2(p_part,obj_sensor,obj_grid)).
permanent(isa2(p_succ,obj_letter_a,obj_letter_f)).
permanent(isa2(p_succ,obj_letter_b,obj_letter_a)).
permanent(isa2(p_succ,obj_letter_c,obj_letter_b)).
permanent(isa2(p_succ,obj_letter_d,obj_letter_c)).
permanent(isa2(p_succ,obj_letter_e,obj_letter_d)).
permanent(isa2(p_succ,obj_letter_f,obj_letter_e)).

% Rules
rule_body(r1,isa2(p_succ,var_l,var_l2)).
rule_body(r1,s2(c_letter,var_s,var_l2)).
rule_head_causes(r1,s2(c_letter,var_s,var_l)).
